- [List features that work perfectly]

#### Issues Found
- [List problems with severity: P0/P1/P2]

#### Not Tested
- [List untestable items with reason]

### Spanish (es)
[Same structure]

### German (de)
[Same structure]

### Chinese Simplified (zh-Hans)
[Same structure]

### Arabic (ar)
#### RTL-Specific Issues
- [List RTL layout problems]

[Same structure as above]

### Hebrew (he)
#### RTL-Specific Issues
- [List RTL layout problems]

[Same structure as above]

## Critical Issues (P0)
